column5: EH Homies, your Joey Votto signed with my Cincinnati Reds for three years for 38 mil. He deserves it.
Big bucks man o man.....gonna start training the children now
eh homie....Joey Votto signed an extension...you guys always had him
Money well spent They also signed Jay Bruce, got the right side of the field covered
good deal for both the reds and votto. he's a heck of a player, much happier to have him with us as to have to face him.i think the reds will be pretty solid for several years to come.  jason
Chief, Whopper & Jason, I might see you guys at the ol' ballyard in April.
